data.description: ***REDUCED!***  Own your own home & build equity for yourself!  Wonderful 3 bedroom, low maintenance, brick, ranch home with a fenced in yard & patio!  One of the bigger homes in the area with 1,275 square feet including a living room, HUGE family room, & eat-in kitchen.   LVP flooring though out.  Updated kitchen - lots of cabinet & countertop space.  Exterior A/C replaced in 2019.  Furnace, water heater, & kitchen updated in 2014.  **Decorative fireplace does not stay with home**
